'''Suurad''' '''[[Suurah]]''' '''[[Suuratu]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: sura, surah, surat; [[carabi]]: ﺳﻮﺭﺓ; ama wadar ahaan: ﺳﻮﺭ
suwar, sidoo kale sūrah)<ref>"'''Suurad''' '''[[Suurah]]''' '''[[Suuratu]]''' ([[ingiriis]]: sura, surah, surat; [[carabi]]: ﺳﻮﺭﺓ; ama wadar ahaan: ﺳﻮﺭ
suwar, sidoo kale sūrah)"</ref> waa maqaro bog ama bogag [[aayad]]o ka mid ah [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah ee [[Alle]] (s.w.t) ku soo dejiyay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k.h). Kitaabka [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah wuxuu ka kooban yahay [[boqol toban iyo afar Suuradood]] oo u sii kala baxa tiro badan oo [[aayad]]o ah.<ref>"waa maqaro bog ama bogag [[aayad]]o ka mid ah [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah ee [[Alle]] (s.w.t) ku soo dejiyay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] (n.n.k.h)."</ref><ref>"Kitaabka [[Quraan]]ka kariimka ah wuxuu ka kooban yahay [[boqol toban iyo afar Suuradood]] oo u sii kala baxa tiro badan oo [[aayad]]o ah"</ref>

Dhererka Suuradaha Quraanku way kala duwan yihiin, tan ugu gaabani waa Suuratul-[[Al-Kawsar]] oo ka kooban [[aayad|3 aayadood]]; halka suurada ugu dheeri tahay Suuratul-[[Al-Baqara]] oo ka kooban [[aayad|286 aayadood]].<ref>"gaabani waa Suuratul-[[Al-Kawsar]] oo ka kooban [[aayad|3 aayadood]]"</ref><ref>"suurada ugu dheeri tahay Suuratul-[[Al-Baqara]] oo ka kooban [[aayad|286 aayadood]]"</ref>
Boqol toban iyo afarta suuradood ee kitaabka Quraanka kariimka ah waxay kala yihiin [[Suurah|86 suuradood]] oo ah [[Makka|Makki]] iyo [[Madiina|28 Madani]] ah. Kala soocida noocan ah waxaay salka ku heeysaa meesha ay suuraduhu ku soo dageen, oo ka hor intii aanu [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] ka tagin magaalada [[Makkah]] quraanka ku soo dagay waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[Makka|Makki]],<ref>"[[Makkah]] quraanka ku soo dagay waxaa loo yaqaanaa [[Makka|Makki]]"</ref> halka markuu [[Nebi]]gu[[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] u hijrooday magaalada [[Madiina]] waxyigii iyo quraankii ku soo dagay ay noqonayaan [[Medina|Madani]]. 

Hadaba suuradaha[[Makki]]ga ahi waxay ka waramaan [[aakhiro|aakhirada]] iyo xoojinta iimaanka, halka suuradaha [[Madani]]ga ahi ay sharaxaan [[nolol|nolosha]], isku-xidhnaanta iyo is-habeynta bulshada [[Islaam]]ka ah.<ref>"[[aakhiro|aakhirada]] iyo xoojinta iimaanka, halka suuradaha [[Madani]]ga ahi ay sharaxaan [[nolol|nolosha]], isku-xidhnaanta iyo is-habeynta bulshada [[Islaam]]ka ah"</ref>
Marka laga reebo Suuratul-[[Al-Tawba]],<ref>"Suuratul-[[Al-Tawba]]"</ref> dhamaan [[suurah|suuradaha]] kale waxay ku bilaabmaan "[[Alle|Ku Bilaabida Magaca Alle ee Naxariista mid gaar iyo mid guud]]" (ﺑﺴﻢ ﺍﻟﻠﻪ ﺍﻟﺮﺣﻤﻦ ﺍﻟﺮﺣﻴﻢ) ''Bismi Allahi al-Raxmaani al-Raxiimi''.<ref>"[[Alle|Ku Bilaabida Magaca Alle ee Naxariista mid gaar iyo mid guud]]" (ﺑﺴﻢ ﺍﻟﻠﻪ ﺍﻟﺮﺣﻤﻦ ﺍﻟﺮﺣﻴﻢ) ''Bismi Allahi al-Raxmaani al-Raxiimi''.</ref>
Midani waa tan kala soocda isla markaana kala saarta Suuradaha ku jira Kitaabka Quraanka Kariimka ah.

Dhinaca kale, qeyb ka mid ah Suuradaha ama suurada oo dhamaystiran ayaa la akhriyaa wakhtiga lagu gudo jiro tukashada [[salaad]]a taasi oo rakcad kasta lagu bilaabo Suuratul-[[Al-Faatixa]] oo dhamaystiran.<ref>"tukashada [[salaad]]a taasi oo rakcad kasta lagu bilaabo Suuratul-[[Al-Faatixa]] oo dhamaystiran"</ref> 
=== Sharaxaada Suurad ===

Erayga suurat waxaa markii ugu horeeysay isticmaalay [[Nebi Muxamed]][[File:Mohamed peace be upon him.svg|18px]] si uu ugu kala saaro iyo kala sooco qeybaha Quraanka kariimka ah. Taasi oo ku dhex jirta aayado [[Alle]] (s.w.t) soo dajiyey sida ku cad 24:1 "Waxaanu kugu soo dejinay suurado wata cadaymo, iyo waxaanu kugu soo dirney calaamado, calaamado cad-cad, kuwaasi oo si farxad leh aad ku xasuusani."<ref>"aayado [[Alle]] (s.w.t) soo dajiyey sida ku cad 24:1 "Waxaanu kugu soo dejinay suurado wata cadaymo, iyo waxaanu kugu soo dirney calaamado, calaamado cad-cad, kuwaasi oo si farxad leh aad ku xasuusani.""</ref>
Dhinaca kale, wadarta suurad waa suwar sida ku xusan Quraanka kariimka, aayadahan oo fasirka af-[[Soomaali]] ku noqonaya "Ma waxay dhaheen isagaa Allifay? Ku dheh "La yimaada toban suwar oo la mid ah (waa Quraankee) una yeedha cid kasta marka laga reebo Alle, haddii aad run sheegaysaan."<ref name="robinson2003">{{cite book|last=Robinson|first=Neal|title=Discovering the Qurʼan: A Contemporary Approach to a Veiled Text|year=2003|publisher=Georgetown University Press|isbn=1589010248|pages=25–97|url=http://www.youquran.com/DISCOVERING-QURAN-Robinson.PDF}}</ref><ref>[http://www.qran.org/q-chrono.htm Qran.org: Quran Verses in Chronological Order]</ref><ref>[http://www.bombaxo.com/chronsurs.html Chronological Order of Quranic Surahs], by Kevin P. Edgecomb (2002).</ref>
